These transcripts were downloaded from the U.S. Supreme Court website and logged in our spreadsheet.

Any corrections have been noted under Corrected Transcripts, and match failures have been logged under Unmatched Transcripts. In addition, transcripts that don’t have exact matches in OYEZ have been noted under Missing OYEZ Transcripts.
